# TradeEdge — environment configuration
#
# LEAVE BOTH BLANK to run fully local (data in your browser, no account).
# FILL BOTH IN to run on Supabase (cloud sync + sign-in across devices).
#
# Find these in your Supabase project: Settings → API.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
